events.name: Awakening of the Guardians and the Role of the Returned of the Anunnaki
events.description: In 2006, Laura Eisenhower, the great granddaughter of President Dwight D. Eisenhower, was approached by a secretive group wanting to recruit her to go to Mars. Eisenhower learned that the Mars project was headed by Dr. Hal Puthoff, who was very familiar with exotic technologies used to ferry personnel and supplies to bases on Mars […]

generated_content.title: Historical Mysteries in Awakening, Humboldt County - Tours & Services
generated_content.description: Awakening, Humboldt County is a mysterious location where the Anunnaki returned to reclaim their lost civilization. This site has been shrouded in secrecy for centuries, but recent discoveries have sparked widespread interest. Visitors can explore ancient ruins, museums, and cryptic artifacts that hint at an otherworldly presence.
